Compare NAMESPACE exports between specific packages versions

Source: R/comapre.R
pac_compare_exports.Rd

using the remote github CRAN mirror to compare NAMESPACE exports between specific packages versions.

pac_compare_exports(
  pac,
  old = NULL,
  new = NULL,
  lib.loc = NULL,
  repos = "https://cran.rstudio.com/"
)

Arguments

pac

character a package name.
old

character an old version of package.
new

character a new version of package.
lib.loc

character. Default: NULL
repos

character the base URL of the repositories to use. Default https://cran.rstudio.com/

Value

list with two slots, added and removed

Note

The comparison is only about exports.

Examples

pac_compare_exports("memoise", "0.2.1", "2.0.0")
#> memoise:0.2.1 vs 2.0.0
#> $removed
#> character(0)
#> 
#> $added
#> [1] "cache_filesystem" "cache_gcs"        "cache_memory"     "cache_s3"        
#> [5] "drop_cache"       "has_cache"        "timeout"         
#> 
pac_compare_exports("shiny", "1.4.0", "1.6.0")
#> shiny:1.4.0 vs 1.6.0
#> $removed
#> character(0)
#> 
#> $added
#>  [1] "MockShinySession"        "bindCache"              
#>  [3] "bindEvent"               "devmode"                
#>  [5] "getCurrentTheme"         "get_devmode_option"     
#>  [7] "httpResponse"            "in_devmode"             
#>  [9] "markdown"                "moduleServer"           
#> [11] "quoToFunction"           "reactiveConsole"        
#> [13] "registerThemeDependency" "runTests"               
#> [15] "shinyAppTemplate"        "tabPanelBody"           
#> [17] "testServer"              "updateActionLink"       
#> [19] "with_devmode"           
#>
